{%- comment -%}
/**
 * Enhanced Collapsible Tabs Section - Multi-Language Accordion Component
 * 
 * This section provides a comprehensive collapsible tabs/accordion component with advanced
 * multi-language support, perfect for FAQs, product information, or any content that
 * benefits from organized, space-saving presentation.
 * 
 * CORE FEATURES:
 * - Multi-language accordion/tabs interface
 * - Dynamic language detection and content switching
 * - Multiple block types (content, button, question/answer)
 * - Responsive accordion-style interface
 * - Image support within content blocks
 * - Custom Liquid content integration
 * - Smooth animations and transitions
 * - Accessibility-compliant with ARIA attributes
 * - Customizable styling with CSS variables
 * 
 * MULTILINGUAL SUPPORT:
 * - Automatic locale detection (German, French, Finnish)
 * - Dynamic language suffix generation (_de, _fr, _fi)
 * - Fallback to default content if localized version unavailable
 * - Localized titles, content, and answers for all block types
 * - Multi-language section headings
 * 
 * BLOCK TYPES:
 * - Content Block: Static text/HTML content with optional images and custom Liquid
 * - Button Block: Call-to-action buttons with custom links and styling
 * - Question Block: Expandable Q&A sections with dual answer support and images
 * 
 * CONTENT MANAGEMENT:
 * - Rich text editor support for all content fields
 * - Custom Liquid code integration for dynamic content
 * - Image picker support with responsive rendering
 * - Dual answer support for complex Q&A scenarios
 * - Additional image support for enhanced visual content
 * 
 * TECHNICAL FEATURES:
 * - Custom web component (details-disclosure) for enhanced functionality
 * - Semantic HTML structure with proper ARIA roles and attributes
 * - CSS animations with motion-safe considerations
 * - Responsive design with mobile-first approach
 * - Accessible keyboard navigation
 * - Focus management for screen readers
 * 
 * CUSTOMIZATION OPTIONS:
 * - Configurable section headings with multi-language support
 * - Flexible block ordering and arrangement
 * - Custom styling through CSS variables
 * - Responsive image handling
 * - Animation control through theme settings
 * 
 * DEPENDENCIES:
 * 
 * Liquid Snippets:
 * - snippets/animation-attrs.liquid - Animation attribute management for sections
 * - snippets/image.liquid - Responsive image rendering with optimization
 * 
 * Note: The following snippets are referenced but may be defined inline or in theme core:
 * - 'responsive-image' - Referenced but file not found (likely using 'image' snippet instead)
 * - 'localized-value' - Referenced but not actively used in current implementation
 * 
 * Custom Elements:
 * - details-disclosure - Custom web component for enhanced disclosure functionality
 *   (Implementation likely in theme's main JavaScript or inline)
 * 
 * Layout Dependencies:
 * - layout/theme.liquid - Contains animation settings and theme configuration
 * 
 * Template Dependencies:
 * - Used in various page templates including FAQ pages and product information sections
 * 
 * External Dependencies:
 * - Shopify Liquid templating engine
 * - CSS custom properties for theming
 * - Modern browser support for custom elements
 * - Intersection Observer API for animations (via animation-attrs)
 * 
 * BROWSER SUPPORT:
 * - Modern browsers with Custom Elements API support
 * - CSS Grid and Flexbox for layout
 * - Progressive enhancement for older browsers
 * - Accessible navigation with keyboard support
 * 
 * PERFORMANCE CONSIDERATIONS:
 * - Lazy loading for images
 * - Conditional animation loading based on theme settings
 * - Minimal DOM manipulation
 * - Efficient language detection and content switching
 * - Optimized CSS with minimal specificity
 * 
 * ACCESSIBILITY FEATURES:
 * - ARIA labels and roles for screen readers
 * - Keyboard navigation support (Enter, Space, Arrow keys)
 * - Focus management for disclosure panels
 * - Semantic HTML structure with proper heading hierarchy
 * - High contrast support
 * - Motion-safe animations
 * 
 * USAGE EXAMPLES:
 * - FAQ sections with multi-language support
 * - Product information accordions
 * - Help documentation with expandable sections
 * - Terms and conditions with organized content
 * - Multi-step processes with collapsible instructions
 */
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- assign locale_code = request.locale.iso_code -%}
{%- assign lang_map = 'de,fr,fi' | split: ',' -%}
{%- assign lang_suffix = '' -%}
{%- if lang_map contains locale_code -%}
  {%- assign lang_suffix = '_' | append: locale_code -%}
{%- endif -%}

<div class="container" {%- render 'animation-attrs', attrs: 'data-cc-animate' -%}>
  <div class="collapsible-tabs">
    {% if section.settings.title != blank %}
      <h3 class="collapsible-tabs__heading collapsible-tabs__content" id="faq-{{ section.settings.title | handle }}">
        {%- assign title_field = 'title' | append: lang_suffix -%}
        {%- assign title_value = section.settings[title_field] -%}
        {%- if title_value != blank -%}
          {{ title_value }}
        {%- else -%}
          {{ section.settings.title }}
        {%- endif -%}
      </h3>
    {% endif %}

    {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
      <div class="collapsible-tabs__block" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
        {% if block.type == 'content' %}
          <div class="collapsible-tabs__text collapsible-tabs__content rte">
            {%- assign content_field = 'content' | append: lang_suffix -%}
            {%- assign content_value = block.settings[content_field] -%}
            {%- if content_value != blank -%}
              {{ content_value }}
            {%- else -%}
              {{ block.settings.content }}
            {%- endif -%}

            {{ block.settings.liquid_content }}

            {% if block.settings.image != blank %}
              {%
                render 'responsive-image',
                image: block.settings.image,
                alt: block.settings.title | escape,
                sizes: "100vw",
                class: "collapsible-tabs__image"
              %}
            {% endif %}
          </div>

        {% elsif block.type == 'button' %}
          <div class="collapsible-tabs__button collapsible-tabs__content">
            <a class="btn btn--primary btn--link" href="{{ block.settings.link }}"
              ><span class="btn__text">{{ block.settings.title | escape }}</span></a
            >
          </div>

        {% elsif block.type == 'question' %}
          <div class="collapsible-tabs__tab">
            <details-disclosure>
              <details
                class="disclosure"
                id="detail-{{ block.id }}"
                aria-expanded="false"
                data-accordion
              >
                <summary
                  class="disclosure__title"
                  role="button"
                  aria-controls="content-{{ block.id }}"
                  aria-expanded="false"
                >
                  {%- assign title_field = 'title' | append: lang_suffix -%}
                  {%- assign title_value = block.settings[title_field] -%}
                  {%- if title_value != blank -%}
                    {{ title_value }}
                  {%- else -%}
                    {{ block.settings.title }}
                  {%- endif -%}
                </summary>
                <div
                  id="content-{{ block.id }}"
                  class="disclosure__panel has-motion"
                  aria-labelledby="detail-{{ block.id }}"
                >
                  <div class="disclosure__content rte">
                    {%- assign answer_field = 'answer' | append: lang_suffix -%}
                    {%- assign answer_value = block.settings[answer_field] -%}
                    {%- if answer_value != blank -%}
                      {{ answer_value }}
                    {%- else -%}
                      {{ block.settings.answer }}
                    {%- endif -%}

                    {{ block.settings.liquid_content }}

                    {% if block.settings.image != blank %}
                      {%
                        render 'responsive-image',
                        image: block.settings.image,
                        alt: block.settings.title | escape,
                        sizes: "100vw",
                        class: "collapsible-tabs__image"
                      %}
                    {% endif %}

                    {%- assign answer_2_field = 'answer_2' | append: lang_suffix -%}
                    {%- assign answer_2_value = block.settings[answer_2_field] -%}
                    {%- if answer_2_value != blank -%}
                      <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
                        {{ answer_2_value }}
                      </div>
                    {%- elsif block.settings.answer_2 != blank -%}
                      <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
                        {{ block.settings.answer_2 }}
                      </div>
                    {%- endif -%}

                    {% if block.settings.image_2 != blank %}
                      {%
                        render 'responsive-image',
                        image: block.settings.image_2,
                        alt: block.settings.title | escape,
                        sizes: "100vw",
                        class: "collapsible-tabs__image"
                      %}
                    {% endif %}
                  </div>
                </div>
              </details>
            </details-disclosure>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .collapsible-tabs__tab .disclosure__title {
    padding-top: 20px;
    padding-bottom: 20px;
    border: 0;
    font-size: 1em;
    font-weight: 700;
    position: relative;
    padding-right: 40px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  details[open] .disclosure__title:after {
    transform: translateY(-50%) rotate(45deg);
  }

  .collapsible-tabs__image {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    margin-top: 15px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    display: block;
  }

  .disclosure__title:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid currentColor;
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .collapsible-tabs {
    max-width: var(--reading-container-width, 800px);
    margin: var(--section-padding) auto;
  }
  .collapsible-tabs .disclosure {
    margin: 0;
    border: 0;
  }

  .collapsible-tabs__tab {
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }
  .collapsible-tabs__tab .disclosure__title {
    padding-top: 20px;
    padding-bottom: 20px;
    border: 0;
    font-size: 1.3em;
  }
  .collapsible-tabs__tab p:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  .collapsible-tabs__tab p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .collapsible-tabs__heading {
    margin-top: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .collapsible-tabs__text {
    margin-top: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .collapsible-tabs__button {
    margin-top: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
</style>

